Mauritian orchid sightings

orchid.Rd

Mauritian orchid (Angraecum aff. rutenbergianum) sighting record from Solow & Roberts (2003). The temporal range (init.time to test.time) of these data is 1933 to 1996. Format: ccon.

Usage

orchid

Format

A numeric vector with 11 values.

References

Key Reference

Solow, A. R., & Roberts, D. L. (2003). A nonparametric test for extinction based on a sighting record. Ecology, 84(5), 1329-1332. doi:10.1890/0012-9658(2003)084[1329:ANTFEB]2.0.CO;2
